author: ETA PRIME
description:
Valve’s standalone Steam Machine isn't coming until 2026. I didn't want to wait, so I built a custom SFF rig that crushes 1440p gaming right now.
In this build, we are mixing the brand new Intel Core Ultra 5 245K with an AMD Radeon RX 7600 to create a fully SteamOS-ready console killer. It’s small, it’s powerful, and unlike the mobile chips in handhelds, this desktop hardware chews through Cyberpunk 2077, Elden Ring, and even Marvel Rivals. I’ll walk you through the parts, the build process in the Jonsbo NV12 case, and benchmarks on the latest games.
